    "Html": "That is exactly what I was looking for.<br>\r\nIt looks like we have to roll our own.<br>\r\nThere is a section in the help guide under Technical Concepts / Commands / Extending Command Support<br>\r\nthat describes how to do it.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMaybe someone will post some sample code for us.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTerrence\r\n",
