    "Id": "167108",
    "ThreadId": "49918",
    "Html": "Yes, if you want to bind event X on control Y to a control, you will have to roll your own. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHowever, for your situation, there is a much easier solution. You can two way bind a property of your ViewModel to the SelectedItem of your Combobox. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHope this helps. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n_Erwin\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2009-03-11T15:32:59.223-07:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
